---
layout: base.njk
title: Tags
description: Browse tags for Azure, GitHub, policy, operations, and web engineering notes.
keywords: tags, Azure, GitHub, policy, operations, web engineering
permalink: /tags/
---
<section>
  <h1>Tags</h1>
  <ul class="tag-index tag-cloud" role="list">
    {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
      <li class="tag-cloud-item">
        <a href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/" aria-label="#{{ tag }} ({{ (collections[tag] or []) | length }} posts)">
          <span>#{{ tag }}</span>
          <span class="tag-count" aria-hidden="true">{{ (collections[tag] or []) | length }}</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>